snippet.title: Best VGM 921 - Soul Calibur II - Raise Thy Sword (Nightmare's Theme)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gamecube / Xbox / PS2
Soul Calibur II (2003)
Raise Thy Sword (Nightmare's Theme)
Yoshihito Yano
